│ CostCtx, OrigLoop) ||\n                                                       │
│ planContainsAdditionalSimplifications(getPlanFor(LegacyVF.Width),\n           │
│ CostCtx, OrigLoop)) &&\n         \" VPlan cost model and legacy cost model    │
│ disagreed\");\n\nThis extends the assertion to allow disagreement when either │
│ VF would not generate vector instructions, which is consistent with the VPlan │
│ selection loop earlier that skips such VFs. This avoids asserting on benign   │
│ differences that arise purely from willGenerateVectors filtering.\n\n5.       │
