│ of the contenders, similar to how the VPlan path already filters them.        │
│                                                                               │
│ 4. Proposed Edit Point(s):                                                    │
│ Modify the assertion in computeBestVF to also tolerate disagreements when     │
│ either the VPlan or legacy-selected VF would not actually generate vector     │
│ instructions, aligning the assertion's exception conditions with the VPlan    │
│ gating:                                                                       │
│                                                                               │
│ Edit file llvm/lib/Transforms/Vectorize/LoopVectorize.cpp lines 7579-7584:    │
│ - Current:                                                                    │
│   assert((BestFactor.Width == LegacyVF.Width || PlanForEarlyExitLoop ||       │
│           planContainsAdditionalSimplifications(getPlanFor(BestFactor.Width), │
│                                                 CostCtx, OrigLoop) ||         │
│           planContainsAdditionalSimplifications(getPlanFor(LegacyVF.Width),   │
│                                                 CostCtx, OrigLoop)) &&        │
