│ This extends the assertion to allow disagreement when either VF would not     │
│ generate vector instructions, which is consistent with the VPlan selection    │
│ loop earlier that skips such VFs. This avoids asserting on benign differences │
│ that arise purely from willGenerateVectors filtering.                         │
